<s> This is indeed illegal.  </s>
<s> The simplest fix is to move the script into the table cell.  </s>
<s> You could also rewrite your script to avoid the processing error.  </s>
<s> Tidy isn't smart as a human and doesn't have enough common sense to "know" that this is a good thing to do.  </s>
<s> For instance, it doesn't understand hardly anything about JavaScript.  </s>
